<br>
BTW, Creator is on tier-5 and AL is on tier-7.  Neither of these are &quot;guards&quot; for the tier, though.  The guard for 5 is Tunare.  The guard for 6 is AoW.  The guard for 7 is the cursed and 8 is the emporer.  Typically, the guard for the tier is the hardest beast in the tier.  My comment on ST was that sometimes what tier they put things in doesn't make sense.  Making ST tier-2, which is guarded by Vindi, is ridiculously low.<br>
<br>
Anyway, if you didn't slay AoW, you are not tier-6.  So what?  The damn tiers are only an arbitrary pain in the ass Legends creation and have nothing at all to do with any other server.  Just say you're NTOV/Ssra capable and everyone will know what you mean.  Emulating Legends on a non-legends server is weird.  It makes you look like legends wannabes, which is pretty far from what you are from what I can tell. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=decius1@firionavie>Decius1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 82<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/22/02 11:12:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1610.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_tongue.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re:</span><hr size=1> Top guild currently is Resolution. There's not much room for debate their. Neither is that a source of shame to FnF. FnF have been top in the past, and may well be in the future.<br>
